ğŸ”„ Main Formula (Ohm's Law & Power Law)

\text{Power (W)} = \text{Voltage (V)} \times \text{Current (A)}

\text{Current (A)} = \frac{\text{Power (W)}}{\text{Voltage (V)}} î€


